{
  "texts": [
    "DELD is a model-agnostic method that can be injected into any pre-trained language model.",
    "The training aimed to fine-tune the soft prompts while maintaining the frozen parameters of the pre-trained model.",
    "In this work, we use the BERT-base and T5-base models from HuggingFace Transformers as the backbone.",
    "The learning rate is set to 1e-3.",
    "We fine-tune the models for 10 epochs."
  ]
}